# gooos/.dockerignore
#
# The Dockerfile clones a fresh master from github.com/ryogrid/gooos
# inside the image, so the build context is mostly unused. Keep the
# context small anyway in case someone runs `docker build .` from a
# working tree with a populated tmp/ — sending multi-MiB ISO/object
# files into the daemon for nothing is wasteful.

# Build artifacts
tmp/
user/build/

# Saved Docker image (excluded from git too — see .gitignore)
gooos-dev.tar.gz

# Local Claude Code state
.claude/

# Local scratch
hoge.md
TODO.md

# Backup archive of reference docs
62cc81656d955f9c12cc7ee4f4c083c7-*.zip
62cc81656d955f9c12cc7ee4f4c083c7-*/
